title: 12/27/21 DPS Hour 2 Albert Breer

description:
Jason & Geoff talk about Jonathan Allen’s sideline fight with his teammate and his comments after the game, Bill Belichick and his (lack of) New Year’s Resolutions, if the Packers season has changed the way Rodgers feels about the team, Sports Illustrated & MMQB’s Albert Breer joins the show, and more!
